snippet.title: Daniel Schmachtenberger - Designing A System That Naturally Cares (WeRiseUP)
snippet.description:
Do you believe it's possible for us to create a world where are all naturally inclined to be stewards of the Cosmos? Researcher and Co-Founder of Neurohacker Collective Daniel Schmachtenberger shares why he believes it to be critical that we do! #weriseup

Learn more about what Daniel and the Neurohacker team have developed and are working on by visiting neurohacker.com and join the WeRiseUP movement today to get FREE access to exclusive interviews with Jack Canfield, Alanis Morissette and more now at weriseup.com/social
